    dc:creator "Hesler, Louis S.; Gates, Michael W.; Beckendorf, Eric A." ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "New records document Cystiphora sonchi (Vallot) (Diptera: Cecidomyiidae) and associated parasitoids (Hymenoptera) in the continental United States" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565507>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565509>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565511>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565513> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565507>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Distribution map of Cystiphora sonchi in North America. Pink indicates Canadian provinces with previous records of C. sonchi and orange indicates states with new records in the USA." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4565507/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565509>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Sowthistle leaves with pustule galls of Cystiphora sonchi. A) International Falls, Minnesota, USA, in 2019.B–C) Heavily galled leaves near Brookings, South Dakota, USA, in 2018." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4565509/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565511>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Individual pustule galls on Sonchus arvensis with variable numbers of larval Cystiphora sonchi per gall." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4565511/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4565513>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Hymenoptera associated with pustule galls of Cystiphora sonchi. A) Aprostocetus cf. atticus. B) Lyrcus," ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4565513/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

